                <h1>About Us</h1><hr>
                <p><span>B</span>lessFresh is a startup by bunch of professionals to bring creativity and transformation in the distribution system of Daily needs, groceries, fruits and vegetables to B2C in the first phase and then subsequently to non-veg minimally processed Ready to Cook products. The ultimate objective of the company is not on selling products rather optimizing the entire logistics chain to reach fresh product directly from producers to consumer in the least possible time through application of IT.  Bless Fresh is going to create a backward integration also, with collection and primary processing and packaging center, where there will be direct procurement from the farmers and this activity will enhance rural income.</p>
                <p>Bless Fresh is a Social Enterprise, there has been deliberate effort  to bring employment among the tribal and rural women from Jharkhand ranging from illiterate to collage/ School drop outs. They will be trained at Revotech Institute for Rural Development, Ranchi, which is going to open very shortly to enable rural folk towards livelihood generation through competency enhancement. The Centre will focus on utilizing the rural competency at every step value chain. Most of the staff in Bless Fresh are from rural and tribal background of Jharkhand. With this venture the stakeholders are trying to give employment to the rural people from Jharkhand specially tribal and women to enhance their livelihood income.</p>
                <p>The company is coming up with the concept of Chain of Neighbourhood Retail Store in a small format with the estimation that 70% of its business volume will through home delivery and 30% from walk in customers. The company encourage its customer to use apps for the delivery to avoid any physical contact. Any order received before 12.00 AM in the night will be delivered next morning on or before 6 AM.</p>
                <p>Bless Fresh is committed to the Society to bring product which has value for money and no compromise on quality.</p>
                <p><strong>Some innovative concept of Basket has been designed to take care of the daily need, weekly need and monthly need, each basket will have its USP in terms of the delivery time:</strong></p>
                <p><strong>Morning Basket:</strong> It includes daily essentials such as Milk, Baby foods, Bread and Bakery Products, Fruits and Vegetables, Frozen and Ready to Cook Products. The delivery time for these items will be within 30 Minutes within the 3 Kilometers of radius. A significant amount of savings will be passed to the customers.</p>
                <p><strong>Weekly Basket:</strong> It will consist of the requirements like Groceries, Dry fruits, Ready to Eat, fruits. Here also the members will have an opportunity to save the significant amount of savings on their purchase.</p>
                <p><strong>Monthly Basket:</strong> The loyal customer will be treated as a member and a separate account will be maintained for the customers with a assigned code and any monthly purchase for more than Rs. 10,000.0 will get an additional benefit other than the regular savings. </p>
            	<p>Therefore, associate with Bless Fresh your regular shopping will change the lives of many people especially the downtrodden and tribal who get limited opportunity on the entire landscape. Lets irrespective of the discount will be passed to the saving  and   essentials goods has been put under Morning Basket Concept.</p>
